data.description: ***SELLERS OFFERING 5k IN CONCESSIONS.*** Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and Southern charm in this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located right across the street from Logan Martin Lake! Step inside, and you're greeted by a spacious, light-filled living area, where the harmony of everyday life and entertainment thrives. Three generously sized bedrooms offer a peaceful haven for rest and rejuvenation. Each room is a sanctuary with its own unique charm, featuring large windows that invite the warmth of the Southern sun. The allure of this property truly comes to life when you step outside. The expansive 1-acre lot creates a sense of openness and endless possibilities. Imagine the thrill of open-air family gatherings, gardening, bonfires and even the potential for future expansion. On those sweltering Alabama summer days, your very own saltwater pool is the ultimate oasis! LINCOLN SCHOOL SYSTEM!
